Ukrinform correspondent asked him another question after a briefing: "If President Putin summoned you, said that he had collapsed in Ukraine, lost 200,000 soldiers and asked for advice - what would you advise him as a diploma and just a Russian?"

“It is impossible to imagine - that he would ask me, he will not ask me. He has a head on his shoulders, ”the post of Russia replied at the UN.

