* work of multidisciplinary rehabilitation team - from the primary examination and consultation of a specialist, making a rehabilitation diagnosis and forming an individual rehabilitation program for the provision of rehabilitation services; * laboratory and instrumental examinations; * Rehabilitation services regardless of the child's place of residence; * counseling of the child by doctors of other specialties in accordance with its condition; * special screening for the detection of autistic spectrum disorders; * nutrition of the child in the hospital; * Selection and adaptation of special equipment and alternative communication facilities for the child and more.** Read also: ** [](https://www.ukrinform.ua/rubric-society/3598171-v-ukraini-startuvala-programa-rozsirenoi-perevirki-nemovlat-na-ridkisni-zahvoruvanna.html)Full [](https://contracting.nszu.gov.ua/kontraktuvannya/kontraktuvannya-2023/vimogi-pmg-2023)that are included in the package available on the NSAU website in the "Requirements 2023"(paragraph 30 “Medical rehabilitation of infants who were born prematurely and/abysses during the first three years of life”).

Як повідомлялося, в Програмі медичних гарантій на 2023 рік передбачено 39пакетів медичних послуг. Бюджет ПМГ становить понад 142 млрд грн.

