![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-03T21-32-00-03-00/630_360_1585831815-622.jpg)Rehabilitation during the first three years of life for babies, who were born in advance and/or patients, is carried out at 128 hospitals of Ukraine.

This is reported on [](https://moz.gov.ua/article/news/reabilitacija-protjagom-pershih-troh-rokiv-zhittja-dlja-nemovljat-jaki-narodilis-peredchasno-taabo-hvorimi-), reports Ukrinform.

"Medical rehabilitation of children under three years of age, who were born prematurely and/abnormalities, is free of charge in all medical institutions of Ukraine, which have a contract with the NSAU. There are 128 hospitals all over the country. Most in Kyiv, Dnipropetrovsk and Lviv regions," - it reads message.

It is noted that such assistance is provided within the package of the Medical Care Program "Medical care for newborns in difficult neonatal cases". For those who need further rehabilitation, the package "Medical rehabilitation, which were born premature and/or sick during the first three years of life" is provided.

The MoH notes that parents can choose any hospital that has a contract of ZSZU in this direction, regardless of the place of registration [](https://www.ukrinform.ua/tag-diti). It is possible to obtain such a medical assistance with the regulation of the primary care physician with whom the declaration is concluded, with a statement of the attending physician, in case of transfer from another medical establishment of the hospital.

